{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1007/comments/1474720.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/diff/osrf/gazebo:159eaa4f9077..13c66c49874f?path=gazebo%2Fphysics%2Fbullet%2FBulletScrewJoint.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1007/_/diff#comment-1474720"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 1007, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1007.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1007"}}, "title": "implement screw joint in simbody and clean up screw joint constraint in ode"}, "content": {"raw": "Just style, but I'm not very fan of large indentations. I usually propose:\n\n```\n#!c++\n\nif (! this->bulletScrew)\n{\n    gzerr << \"bulletScrew not created yet.\\n\";\n    return;\n}\n\nif (_index == 0)\n...\n```\n\nit helps readability and the detection of bugs. ", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Just style, but I'm not very fan of large indentations. I usually propose:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-c++\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">!</span> <span class=\"k\">this</span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">bulletScrew</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">gzerr</span> <span class=\"o\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;bulletScrew not created yet.</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">_index</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">...</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>it helps readability and the detection of bugs. </p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2014-03-21T00:44:06.671789+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Jose Luis Rivero", "uuid": "{d12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bd12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bd12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/109284c8b83411dbc7492138f6167e9ed=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsJR-5.png"}}, "nickname": "Jose Luis Rivero", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:155a32e2-420c-4d50-98e0-0e722f63f906"}, "inline": {"to": 422, "from": null, "outdated": true, "path": "gazebo/physics/bullet/BulletScrewJoint.cc"}, "updated_on": "2014-03-21T00:44:06.689348+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 1474720}